    39	# dep to carry a `version` requirement so the registry resolver can find
    40	# them once `path` is stripped at publish time. Centralizing the version
    41	# pins here keeps the release substrate (`scripts/set-version.sh`) editing
    42	# one location per axis, not N call-sites.
    43	#
    44	# Axis W entries are bumped lockstep with [workspace.package].version.
    45	# Axis E (fathomdb-embedder-api) carries its independent version per
    46	# dev/design/release.md § Version axes.
